I was fortunate enough to get the #COVID19 #vaccine 3 days ago - only symptom was a mild sore arm - that’s gone now. 

Symptoms are also being tracked by @CDCgov to ensure no unknown or severe side effects. 

Hope we can vaccinate everyone in the world ASAP!
